snippet.title: Disney Twisted-Wonderland KV and Theme Song Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Twisted Wonderland.  Let us show you the real happily-ever-after.

"Disney Twisted-Wonderland" is coming to the US and Canada on January 20, 2022!
 
Pre-registration begins December 21st so head to the official website to learn more!
https://disneytwistedwonderland.com
#twsten #twistedwonderland
